@NODE 8. "Shareware"
                              Shareware.
                              
	This version has a few more restrictions added.
	Registered version has:
		Unlimited phonebook size. (Memory permitting)
		Full 160 character message lengths (Depending on the server
		used.)
		No annoying About requesters on start/quit.
		No appended text added to your messages.

	You will also be added to the AmiGSM userlist and will receive all
	new upgrades via email free.

	To register AmiGSM, send $10 USD cash to the following address.
	Include your name, and email address, and allow upto 14 days for
	proccessing.
	
	Fee:     $10 USD (United States Dollars) Cash only.
